posts.post_title: FS: T-Cards: Uzit, AB460, T210-5, T213-1, T204
posts.post_content:
Miscellaneous T cards for sale - scans of all are available [URL="http://imageevent.com/gspinf/forsaletrade/tcards"]here[/URL].  Some images are included below.

Prices include shipping and assume Paypal (money owed)- check/MO are fine, too.  Email (mikefrohme@yahoo.com) takes priority over posts.  Open to offers on singles/groups if you're interested.

Thanks for looking!

Raw cards - T206's guaranteed to grade or I'll buy 'em back.

T206 (OM) Leifield - SOLD
T206 (PB) Leach (formerly in a PSA 3 slab) - 40
T206 (AB 460) Camnitz (very nice!) - SOLD
T3 Fromme (ad back - frame damage - good clean picture) - 95

T204 Ramly Fromme (Lionel Carter - SGC 30) - SOLD

T212-3 Brackenridge "175 Subjects - Red" (PSA 5) - $130
T213-1 Engle (SGC 30 - tough card in any grade!) - SOLD
